Battera::

She turned from Kup and looked at Windlord. "I appreciate the 
concern. I must admit, my skills in combat are not what they used to 
be. But in time, the combat programs will reboot and I shall be able 
to defend myself a bit more adiquately. I thank you for your concern. 
I am aware of the other factions here. I have been observing them 
from my mountain. I was left behind, so, I was able to sustain myself 
up there."
